<text xml:lang="ta">
  <body>
    <div xml:id="PN230-intro">
      <p type="edition">tiṇai, atu. tuṟai, kaiyaṟunilai. atiyamāṉ takaṭūr porutu vīḻnta eḻiṉiyai aricilkiḻār pāṭiyatu.
      </p>
      <p xml:lang="en" type="translation">  
      </p>
    </div>
    <div xml:id="PN230">
      <lg type="edition">
<l>kaṉṟama rāyaṅ kāṉat talkavum</l>
<l>veṅkāl vampalar vēṇṭupulat tuṟaiyavuṅ</l>
<l>kaḷamali kuppai kāppila vaikavum</l>
<l>vilaṅkupakai kaṭinta kalaṅkāc ceṅkōl</l>
<l>vaiyakam pukaḻnta vayaṅkuviṉai yoḷvāṭ</l>
<l>poyyā veḻiṉi porutukaḷañ cēra</l>
<l>vīṉṟō ṇītta kuḻavi pōlat</l>
<l>taṉṉamar cuṟṟan talaittalai yiṉaiyak</l>
<l>kaṭumpaci kalakkiya viṭumpaikūr neñcamoṭu</l>
<l>nōyuḻantu vaikiya vulakiṉu mikanaṉi</l>
<l>nīyiḻan taṉaiyē yaṟaṉiṟ kūṟṟam</l>
<l>vāḻtaliṉ varūum vayalvaḷa ṉaṟiyāṉ</l>
<l>vīḻkuṭi yuḻavaṉ vittuṇ ṭāaṅ</l>
<l>koruva ṉāruyi ruṇṇā yāyi</l>
<l>ṉērār palluyir paruki</l>
<l>yārkuvai maṉṉōvava ṉamaraṭu kaḷattē.</l>
</lg>
<lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l corresp="1">While the cows desired by [their] calves remain in the forest, </l>
<l corresp="2">while hot-legged travellers stay in the places they want, </l>
<l corresp="3">while the ample heaps on the threshing flooe are kept without guard, </l>
<l corresp="6">as falseless Eḻiṉi after fighting joined the battle field, </l>
<l corresp="4">with [his] just sceptre unperturbed that had chased away bothersome enemies, </l>
<l corresp="5">with [his] bright sword of glowing work[manship] that was praised by the world, </l>
<l corresp="8">while his battle troups despair one by one, </l>
<l corresp="7">like a calf that was left by her who bore it, </l>
<l corresp="10">very much more than the world which is kept enduring pain, </l>
<l corresp="9">with hearts abounding in distress when afflicted with fierce hunger, </l>
<l corresp="11">you are lost, virtueless Death. </l>
<l>If, like a ploughman of a sunken clan who does not know </l>
<l>corresp="11-12">the wealth of strength that comes from living,</l>
<l corresp="14">you don’t eat the precious life of one man, </l>
<l corresp="15">will you drink up the many lives of the enemies </l>
<l corresp="16">[and] be satiated, on the battle field where he abides? </l>
</lg>
    </div>
